    <div>
      <p>Kiddush started as a wineclub in 2021 and has, since then developed into a beer breweri. We are producing the beer ourselves in our little breweri in the Northern region of Zealand.</p>
      <p>
        Our passion for brewing beer stems from our desire to bring people together and create a sense of community. We believe that there's something special about sharing a pint of delicious,
        locally-brewed beer with friends and loved ones, and that's what drives us to keep experimenting and perfecting our craft.
      </p>
