    <div class="max800 jacob">
      <h2 class="place_right">JACOB</h2>
      <img class="jacob_img" src="/img/portraitjacob.webp" alt="potrait of co-owner, Jacob" />
      <p>
        Jacob is 24 years old and started Kiddush in 2021 . It all began when Jacob got tired of everything being so fancy while working as a cellare. Gathering people around good beer for a
        reasonable price became a misson.
        <br />
        <br />
        Jacob has a good sense for graphic design and does’nt put anything in production that he can’t stand by. A thouroughly developed product from beginning to end is the most important thing for Jakob
        as co-owner of Kiddush.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="max800 lucas">
      <h2 class="place_left">LUCAS</h2>
      <img class="lucas_img" src="/img/portraitlucas.webp" alt="portrait of co-owner, Lucas" />
      <p>
        Lucas is 25 years old and grew up in Østerbro, Copenhagen. Good food and a healthy thirst has always been a part of Lucas’ persona. With a passion for brewing and a knack for experimentation,
        he brings a unique and creative perspective to the brewery's operations.
        <br />
        <br />
        His dedication to quality ensures that every sip of Kiddush beer is a delight for the taste buds, and his enthusiasm for community-building makes him a natural fit for the company's mission.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
